dct_title_s: Plan of Governors, Kennedy's & Brown's Islands and Red Hook together with part of the Bay and Soundings, showing the position they bear to each other and to New York
dct_description_sm: Map shows part of New York (The Battery), North River, Bay of New York, Browns Island, Kennedy Island, Bedlow's Island, Notten/Governor's Island, East River, and Red Hook.
